ygData.messageBody:
Halo

Help yourself by going to this web site and requesting the healing
services of this man.

I am a web site creator and am using my mailing list account to tell
everyone about him and his service - what he is doing is wonderful -
truly.

The energy he works with is phenomenal - he is a Sirian being in
human
body and truly is the most gentle loving soul and is here to help.
We
are blest just to have him here on Earth.

He has done so much to help me and so I am telling as many people as
I
can reach because he needs the support of humanity in order to
complete his work.

So many dark forces have attacked him and tried to stop his work - he
truly deserves help - he didn't need to come here - he chose to in
order to help humanity.

For higher dimensional beings to be incarnate on Earth is very
difficult for them - it is like us humans trying to swim and breathe
"mud". He and many others like him have come to Earth to help us
through a tremendous shift that is occurring.

This man - Ra-So Nova is truly Beautiful - in body, mind and soul.

What he has to offer is so heavenly and overwhelming.

It isn't just him though - it is the beings that he works with.

He doesn't know I am doing this and I don't want him ever to know -
he
is very shy and humble actually - it may not seem it when you first
read the web site though.

This man gives so incredibly much and receives so incredibly little
for it. All he wants is to be able to complete his mission on Earth
and then return home to Sirius A.

He doesn't want riches or women or fame or anything - he just wants
to
help raise humanities awareness, to heal the damage of aeons of
negative extraterrestrial abuse and restore humanities ability to
co-create with God.

Please help him to fulfill his work and receive his wonderful gifts.

This is WAY BEYOND Reiki - this is literally the most powerful
healing
and evolutionary service on Earth.

It is offered freely - though It would be nice to offer a donation in
return.

Love - Janice

This is his website:
HOME and DATABOARD of Lord Ra-So Nova
http://members.xoom.com/rasonova
